import seaborn as sns
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

# Age
plt.subplot(1, 2, 1)

plt.title('Age Distribution')
plt.xlabel('Age')

data['income_10k'] = data['income'] / 10000
# Income
plt.subplot(1, 2, 2)

plt.title('Income Distribution')

plt.tight_layout()
